.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-MACAROON-INFO" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-macaroon-info \- list rune-based access credentials
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-macaroon-info
.SH DESCRIPTION
Core Lightning uses rune-based access control rather than macaroons.
This verb calls
.B lightning-cli listaccess
and returns the list of runes with their restrictions.
Returns an error object if the daemon is unreachable or
.B listaccess
is unavailable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"count":N,"runes":[...]}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-version (1),
.BR lightning-daemon (1)
